#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn50.55"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 50 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 50 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:0.2"
msgid "6. Punagaṅgāpeyyālavagga "
msgstr "6. Another Chapter of Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges, Etc. "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:0.3"
msgid "55–66. Pācīnādisutta "
msgstr "55–66. Sloping East, Etc. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.252, sc1
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā pācīnapabbhārā; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the east. "

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañca balāni bhāvento pañca balāni bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the five powers slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.3"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañca balāni bhāvento pañca balāni bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant who develops the five powers slant, slope, and incline to extinguishment? "

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu, saddhābalaṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the powers of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.5"
msgid "evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañca balāni bhāvento pañca balāni bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the five powers slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.6"
msgid "Vitthāretabbā. "
msgstr "(To be expanded for each of the different rivers as in SN 45.91–102, removal of greed version.) "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.7"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.8"
msgid "Gaṅgāpeyyālavaggo chaṭṭho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.1"
msgid "Cha pācīnato ninnā, "
msgstr "Six on slanting to the east, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.2"
msgid "cha ninnā ca samuddato; "
msgstr "and six on slanting to the ocean; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.3"
msgid "Dvete cha dvādasa honti, "
msgstr "these two sixes make twelve, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.4"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti. "
msgstr "and that’s how this chapter is recited."

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
